Description: 
    Execute power menu options.

Usage: xl-power <Option>

Option: One of the following:

    -h , --help:
        Print this help page.

    -s , --suspend 
        Lock screen then suspend.

    -l , --lock:
        Lock screen.

    -o , --logout:
        Log out.

    -p , --poweroff:
        Power off.

    -r , --reboot:
        Reboot.

    -z , --sleep:
        Suspend without screen locking.
